query:
SELECT 
  sourceType,
  COUNT(*) as count,
  SUM(CASE WHEN upsetBidCloseDate IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_date
FROM properties 
WHERE saleStatus = 'in_upset_period'
GROUP BY sourceType
ORDER BY count DESC
